Odaily Planet Daily News According to the monitoring of on-chain analyst Yu Jin, a whale is suspected of using the market fluctuations caused by the 50x leverage whale buying and selling operations on Hyperliquid to arbitrage. He borrowed LINK to sell when the "Hyperliquid 50x Whale" bought LINK spot in the afternoon, and then withdrew LINK from Binance to pay it back; 
1 hour ago, the 50x leverage whale on Hyperliquid sold PAXG and continued to increase its position in LINK, so he bought PAXG on the chain and transferred it to Binance to sell; 
Half an hour ago, when the 50x leverage whale on Hyperliquid continued to increase its position in LINK, he continued to borrow 500,000 LINK (7.2 million US dollars) from Aave and then transferred it to Binance, which should also be sold in Binance.
